[SN]TITLE[SN]
Lionel Shriver: Why the term 'populism' is dishonest

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Viewsnight is BBC Newsnight's new place for ideas and opinion.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
1 February 2017 Last updated at 16:25 GMT
Here US journalist and author Lionel Shriver argues the term "populist" is loaded - and has become code for "ignorant" or "pig thick".
